{"tid":1556984,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<831>警方澄清謠言受質疑　專家指政府可以解釋時間不多  一旦時機過去  市民將不會接納任何說法","createTime":"2019-09-10T02:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T05:10:01.000Z","uid":35790,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd792f0996d8882f59f1e6202d2827f5a11ad9f","tid":1556984,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"心理學會前會長張傳義：傳言出現顯示對政府信任正瓦解<br />\n<br />\n2019-09-09<br />\n<br />\n自8.31太子站警方清場後，出現懷疑有人被打死的傳言，政府已作出澄清。香港心理學會前會長張傳義表示，傳言的出現顯示市民對政府或公營機構的信任正瓦解，當市民對相關機構失去信心，便更偏向相信自己接收的資訊來理解事件的真相。<br />\n<br />\n張傳義接受本台節目《千禧年代》電話訪問時表示，就政治心理學而言，政府與市民間的信任支柱正消失，當政府的言行不一致，譬如表示希望與社會對話，但沒有相關行為配合，市民便對政府的說法越會懷疑，對政府的管治形成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">張傳義表示，現時管治情況未到最惡劣的時候，因為市民仍相信閉路電視片段提供真相， 政府只要提供有力證據，市民仍偏向相信。但他形容，政府可以解釋的時間不多，一旦時機過去，市民將不會接納任何說法。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479595-20190909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479595-20190909.htm&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=3023aea1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479595-20190909.htm&h=6ba0b6b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479595-20190909.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a7c240d20defa27d2bceefbd5a199bb70079071f","tid":1556984,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:53:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">九七移交 承認錯誤 拿出勇氣 奮力一戰 止黑治港</span><br />\nIn 1997 return China is false , Fight for Freedom and Democracy Defend HomeLand of Brave ."},{"pid":"5b4bdd650205209b7061745de5c9957a5a1fa6f6","tid":1556984,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"已經過咗10日<br />\n錄影帶可信性已低"},{"pid":"47069cb1232866e03498cab67013c32c7e645705","tid":1556984,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"acd1cabb617eff46beda8cf20b1503d2e852c74e","tid":1556984,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=7cc7f7f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"3af4d156ea2bbbb474b9b596cfe042e9c636abce","tid":1556984,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}